#: admin/class-ageverif-admin.php
msgid "These are search-engine and AI crawlers. Ticking them means these bots see your full HTML — important for SEO. Leave all ticked unless you want a specific bot to see the gate too."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-ageverif-admin.php
msgid "Where to send visitors who fail or close the gate — a friendly “you must be 18+ to enter” page is better than a dead end. Works alongside “Closable Gate” above."
